last_episode_to_air.overview: A penthouse party provides the perfect cover for the girls to relocate their equipment. Tryst resorts to drastic measures when his own plans go awry.

name: Fakes
overview: Teenage best friends Zoe and Becca set out to build their own fake ID empire, but when business starts booming, their life of crime gets way too real.

episodes.name: Teen Drinking is Very Bad...
episodes.overview: Impressed by Zoe's fake ID, Becca asks for one of her own — setting in motion the criminal events that follow. At least that's how Zoe remembers it.

episodes.name: ...Yo I got a Fake I.D. though
episodes.overview: Becca shares her side of the story, recalling how their fake ID business got started — and how it was all Zoe's idea.

episodes.name: Don't Panic. (definitely don't)
episodes.overview: Zoe and Becca scramble to produce hundreds of fake IDs in a short amount of time, but as the clock winds down, problems — and threats — arise.

episodes.name: WE ARE THE CAPTAINS NOW
episodes.overview: As Zoe melts down over production issues and a looming deadline, Becca shows off her business acumen by cleverly troubleshooting their problems.

episodes.name: Real G's Move in Silence like Lasagna
episodes.overview: A busy day in the life of Tryst reveals him juggling multiple hustles in an attempt to go legit. Could Zoe and Becca's business plan change his fortunes?

episodes.name: A Cup of Ambition
episodes.overview: When quirky new hire Sally accidentally loses a bag full of fakes, Zoe and Becca race to track down the IDs before they fall into the wrong hands.

episodes.name: All Eyes On Me
episodes.overview: Worried about potential blowback over the wayward IDs, Zoe and Becca hatch a plan to head off trouble. But as pressure mounts, their friendship frays.

episodes.name: King of Anything
episodes.overview: As Zoe takes on more both at home and at the office, her new responsibilities give her a confidence boost that starts attracting attention.

episodes.name: Forged in Stone (or something)
episodes.overview: Amid relationship troubles, Becca confronts her father. Later, the girls reconnect with Sally and question their business arrangement with Tryst.

episodes.name: She said, she said
episodes.overview: A penthouse party provides the perfect cover for the girls to relocate their equipment. Tryst resorts to drastic measures when his own plans go awry.
